OL,3,CWhat is endometriosis - and why waits
OL,4,Cfor a diagnosis might be speeding up
OL,6,FNHS workers are being issued with new
OL,7,Fguidance to help women with
OL,8,Fendometriosis get diagnosed faster,
OL,9,Fthe National Institute for Health and
OL,10,FCare Excellence (Nice) has announced.
OL,12,FEndometriosis affects 1.5 million
OL,13,Fwomen in the UK, and many face waits
OL,14,Fof up to a decade after symptoms begin
OL,15,Fbefore receiving a formal diagnosis.
OL,17,FDelays in getting diagnosed can
OL,18,Fprolong the suffering of those with
OL,19,Fthe condition, worsen their health and
OL,20,Fbring fertility risks.
