OL,6,F"This Government is determined to
OL,7,Foverhaul women's healthcare and these
OL,8,Fchanges will help patients receive an
OL,9,Faccurate and timely diagnosis,
OL,10,Fbenefitting over a million women."
OL,12,FWhat are the symptoms?
OL,14,FEndometriosis can lead to chronic
OL,15,Fpain, heavy periods, and extreme
OL,16,Ffatigue. It can also cause pain when
OL,17,Fgoing to the toilet.
