OL,3,CWhat is endometriosis - and why waits
OL,4,Cfor a diagnosis might be speeding up
OL,6,FThe condition can also impact
OL,7,Frelationships and fertility, causing
OL,8,Fpain during or after sex and
OL,9,Fdifficulty getting pregnant. It can
OL,10,Falso lead to depression, anxiety and
OL,11,Ffeelings of isolation.
