OL,3,CWhat is endometriosis - and why waits
OL,4,Cfor a diagnosis might be speeding up
OL,6,FProfessor Jonathan Benger, chief
OL,7,Fmedical officer and interim director
OL,8,Fof the Centre for Guidelines at Nice,
OL,9,Fsaid the new advice will help early
OL,10,Fdiagnosis and faster treatment.
OL,12,FHe said: "We recognise that capacity
OL,13,Fin endometriosis clinics remains an
OL,14,Fissue, and that waiting times to be
OL,15,Fseen in secondary care can sometimes
OL,16,Fbe lengthy.
